text: Dmitriy Mironchik (born 25 January 1970) is a Belarusian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belarus Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
